{"word":"ἀνάδειξις","slug":"ἀνάδειξις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνάδειξις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀναδείκνυμι'><el>ἀναδείκνυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a proclamation</i> of an election, <i>an appointment</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>designatio</el>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>(from <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>) <i>a manifestation</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}